text: Do you have any observations about how the negotiations went?
Well, I didn't have much background about past negotiations with the company,...
...but on the basis of my experience, it went very well.
I didn't anticipate any major obstacles going into the negotiations.
We've always managed to make good deals with them in the past.
From my point of view, it seemed both sides were willing to bargain from the outset.
And another factor that helped make quick progress...
...was outlining each party's ideal terms as the meeting got started.
